item.description:
Dinner at Tiki Port Restaurant at 6:30 PM

Cape Cod's #1 Chinese restaurant, Tiki Port has been serving Cape Cod residents and visitors since 1977. Customers return time and time again to share good times as they feast upon the Cantonese, Polynesian/Mandarin, Szechuan cuisines, and to enjoy exotic, tropical drinks from the South Pacific.

 

The Rocky Horror Show to Follow at 8:00 PM

Get dressed up and ready to rock at "The Rocky Horror Show." The camp-y musical parodies B-grade horror movies and tells the story of a newly engaged couple and their encounter with a mad scientist transvestite and his creation, a muscle man named Rocky.

Goodie bags of props will be on sale at the door! Intended for adult audiences. In the Main Theatre of the Tilden Arts Center at Cape Cod Community College, 2240 Iyannough Rd., West Barnstable, MA.

$15 general admission.

Call the Box Office to purchase your own ticket: 508-362-2131 x4044.
